      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3174_0027"/>Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168940">XVIII<unclear>.</unclear>
                  Spöttelga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>se 7</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3174_0028"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb90438">Campo di Carlo Magno</rs></hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="center"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3174_0028"/><date when="1904-08-25">25. Augu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t</date>.</dateline></opener><p><salute><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03452-1"/>M. l.<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03452-1">Mein lieber</note> Freund,</salute><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03452-2"/>kenn<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Du <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb427">Madonna di Campiglio</rs></hi><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03452-2"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> hatte im Vorjahr, vom <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="date-only" target="1903-08-17"/> auf den
                     <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="date-only" target="1903-08-18"/>, in
                  dem <rs type="place" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb427">Ort</rs> übernachtet und war
                  von dort zu einem Treffen mit <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11485">Goldmann</rs>
                  geradelt.</note>? Ein herrlicher Ort. Kö<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>te Wald- und <rs type="place" ref="#pmb117">Alpen</rs>luft. Hätte<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Du nicht Lu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03452-3"/>hierherzukommen<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03452-3">Dazu kam es nicht.</note>? Herzliche Grüße Dir und Deiner <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2173">Frau</rs> Dein <signed>Paul Goldmann</signed></p></div>
      </body>
